OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779027073
OL,3,CPrivate school teacher stRuck off
OL,4,Cafter telling pupil she is 'Premier
OL,5,CLeague'
OL,7,FA PE teacher who told a female student
OL,8,Fthat she was "Premier League" and one
OL,9,Fof his "favourite people on the
OL,10,Fplanet" has been banned from the
OL,11,Fprofession.
OL,13,FStuart Smith who worked at Mayville
OL,14,FHigh School in Southsea in Portsmouth,
OL,15,Fwas excluded from teaching
OL,16,Findefinitely after a disciplinary
OL,17,Fpanel found he had been "overfamiliar"
OL,18,Fand developed an "emotional personal
OL,19,Frelationship" with a pupil.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@]O]qD@HOUrD@GO]yD@YOUyD@fO]zD@
OL,26,AROU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
